int sVpmgp::ipkey

Toggles nonlinearity (set by nonlin)

  • -2: Size-Modified PBE
  • -1: Linearized PBE
  • 0: Nonlinear PBE with capped sinh term [default]
  • >1: Polynomial approximation to sinh, note that ipkey must be odd
